<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
		<title><%= title %></title>
		<!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/base.css"> -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/index.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/faqs.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.typekit.net/jsw5osz.css">
		<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-Zenh87qX5JnK2Jl0vWa8Ck2rdkQ2Bzep5IDxbcnCeuOxjzrPF/et3URy9Bv1WTRi" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script defer src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-OERcA2EqjJCMA+/3y+gxIOqMEjwtxJY7qPCqsdltbNJuaOe923+mo//f6V8Qbsw3" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>      
    </head>
    <body>
        <header class="p-3 bg-dark text-white">
              <div class="d-flex flex-wrap align-items-center justify-content-center justify-content-lg-start">

                <ul class="nav col-12 col-lg-auto me-lg-auto mb-2 justify-content-center mb-md-0">
                  <li><a href="./about" class="nav-link px-2 text-white">About</a></li>
                  <li><a href="./faqs" class="nav-link px-2 text-white">FAQs</a></li>
                  <li><a href="./help" class="nav-link px-2 text-white">Help</a></li>
                </ul>
        
				<h1 id="logo"><a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Goober</a></h1>
				
                <div class="text-end">
				  <a href="/auth/google" id="login"><button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-light me-2">Login</button></a>
                  <a href="./signup"><button type="button" class="btn btn-warning">Sign-up</button></a>
                </div>
              </div>
        </header>

	
		<main>
        <div id="faqsbanner">
          <h1>FAQS</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                  What is Goober?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  Goober is a new rideshare app that provides an alternative to taxis or other rideshare apps. Riders simply click the sign up button on the home page and enter their information. Once you've created an account, you will be able to access the rider portal where you can request a ride.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                  What type of vehicles can be requested for a ride?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  When requesting a ride, riders can select between a sedan, SUV, or a van for their trip.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                  What times can a ride be requested?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  Goober is a 24/7 platform, so a ride can be requested anytime of the day and any day of the week.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                  <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                    What cities can a ride be requested in?
                  </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    Currently, rides can only be requested in metro Atlanta area. We are furiously working on our app to accommodate rides all over the world.
                  </div>
                </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
              <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                Do you screen your drivers to ensure riders safety?
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
              <div class="accordion-body">
                Yes! The safety of our riders is our top priority. Drivers are required to pass a criminal background check, have a clean MVR with no accidents in the last 5 years, have a valid drivers license, and be at least 23 years old. While accidents do happen, we feel that these
                requirements along with our vehicle standards show our commitment to rider's safety.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
              <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                What are your vehicle standards?
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
              <div class="accordion-body">
                All vehicles on the Goober platform must have current registration, current vehicle insurance, be no older than 5 years old, and have no physical damage.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
              <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                How much does a ride cost?
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
              <div class="accordion-body">
                We pride ourselves on providing affordable and safe rides for our customers. Our rides vary from $5-$20. No ride at this time, will exceed $20
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
              <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                Can I reserve a ride for future dates?
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
              <div class="accordion-body">
                Yes, rides can be reserved for future dates.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </main>
	</body>
</html>